These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Birthday: june, august, january, february
Nationality: thai, japanese, spanish, french
1. Birthday:june is on the right of Nationality:spanish##1
2. Nationality:french is on the far left##1
3. Nationality:spanish is between Nationality:japanese and Birthday:august##2
4. Birthday:february is on the far left##1
5. Birthday:january is between Birthday:august and Birthday:june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | february         | august   | january | june       |
| Nationality      | french | thai | spanish   | japanese |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Birthday: february, june, august, october
Flower: begonia, amaryllis, iris, orchid
1. Flower:orchid is between Birthday:august and Flower:amaryllis##2
2. Birthday:october is on the far right##1
3. Flower:iris is on the right of Flower:begonia##1
4. Birthday:february is on the left of Flower:begonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday         | june | february | august | october |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | orchid   | begonia | iris       |

