.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Beverage: coffee, almond-milk, fanta, water
Cigar: prince, baccarat, pall-mall, dunhill
1. Cigar:pall-mall is on the right of Beverage:water##1
2. Cigar:pall-mall is between Cigar:baccarat and Beverage:almond-milk##2
3. Cigar:baccarat is on the far left##1
4. Cigar:dunhill is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1
5. Beverage:almond-milk == Cigar:dunhill##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage          | water    | coffee | almond-milk   | fanta  |
| Cigar   | baccarat | pall-mall   | dunhill | prince |

